# hooks/
#
# Shared React hooks used across multiple features or pages.
# Feature-specific hooks live inside features/<name>/hooks/.
#
# Examples of hooks that will live here (migrated from existing app):
#   hooks/use-auth-state.ts      ← auth session (localStorage → cookie migration needed)
#   hooks/use-mobile.tsx         ← responsive breakpoint detection
#   hooks/use-toast.ts           ← toast notification hook
